{
  "text": "Hence, we have preliminary evidence suggesting that increased mitochondrial fusion occurs in trophoblast cells deprived of amino acids. We propose that this reflects SIMH, a protective mechanism that may be occurring in the LPD placenta [CITATION_1] and in stressed pre-implantation embryos [CITATION_2] .",
